How to interpret it

* If this works, then the C++ probe tools are the broken part
* If this fails, then the host UHD runtime stack itself is broken more generally

My recommendation now

You have enough evidence to stop chasing networking and MPM.

Focus on the host UHD install.

If you want the cleanest fix

Rebuild and install UHD 3.15 fresh in the container, then make sure the runtime picks only that install.

Typical cleanup direction:

rm -rf /usr/local/lib/libuhd*
rm -rf /usr/local/bin/uhd_*
ldconfig

then reinstall from your known-good source tree.

